## Security

- All endpoints: `require_admin` dependency (existing pattern)
- Plan change: only valid enum values accepted (Pydantic `Literal["starter","pro","ultra"]`)
- Bonus attempts: max cap of 100 per skill (prevent abuse)
- Role toggle: cannot demote yourself (admin cannot remove own admin flag)
- Every mutation: writes `admin_audit_logs` row with `old_value_json` / `new_value_json`

