## Open Questions

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Bonus attempts — per-task or global?**
> The current quota system is per-task (e.g., 5 attempts on Task 1, 5 on Task 2).
> Should the bonus be per-task too (admin sets `+3` for Task 1 specifically) or a
> flat global bonus added on top of the total speaking/writing pool?
>
> **Recommendation:** Keep it simple — global bonus per skill for now.
> A per-task override would require a much more complex grid UI.

> [!NOTE]
> **No email/name editing.** Names and emails come from Clerk (the auth provider).
> Editing them here would create a sync mismatch. If you want to support this,
> it requires calling Clerk's Management API separately. Not in scope for this plan.

> [!NOTE]
> **Deleting users is not included.** Deleting is dangerous (cascades attempts,
> reports, purchases) and should go through Clerk's user management with a
> deliberate off-boarding process. Admin can deactivate instead via role removal.
